{"tid":2432434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援者風雨中自發派物資互撐 　七旬翁哽咽：我只係做到呢啲","createTime":"2021-03-04T10:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T11:01:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87f05d58fd23733f0e9e502d89c195c8b0822c6b","tid":2432434,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JYV7VEkqSVUo8MkPZmhlVXGjh4k=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TAVYDMHURZDVHNTX4BGFT4QANA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJYV7VEkqSVUo8MkPZmhlVXGjh4k%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTAVYDMHURZDVHNTX4BGFT4QANA.jpg&h=f9fbf6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批市民捱風抵雨等待審訊結果，不少熱心人士前來為他們送上茶、暖貼、傘、飯盒等物資。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n連續第四天到場聲援的康先生，今日在法院外將一樽樽印有「香港人加油」的樽裝茶，親手向其他同路人送上。外表硬朗的他，提到香港發生的種種不公義，亦不禁眼泛淚光，「我而家70歲⋯⋯仲做到乜嘢？運動我都有出去，睇住啲𡃁仔俾佢哋打！真係自己做唔到，唯有幫手派下嘢，我只係做到呢啲」。他又指，自己連日到場，是為了聲援47名初選被捕者，「依家香港政府係做到諗吓都有罪！仆街，呢個政府係咩政府呀？」<br />\n<br />\n堅守香港鬥長命：睇住中共滅亡！<br />\n康先生形容，今次47人所負上的是莫須有罪名，故對他們能否獲保釋感到不樂觀，又狠批《國安法》紅線太闊，「講一句一生平安都有罪，仲可以點樣？」在訪問中，不時都會感受到康先生對香港的絕望，他更着年輕人不要留在香港，「有能力真係要走」，但表示自己不會考慮移民，會堅守在香港，「留喺度希望同佢鬥長命，睇住中共滅亡！」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/HXCQBGTTC5E4RC72GJQ5FPGDEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FHXCQBGTTC5E4RC72GJQ5FPGDEQ%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=94b78960\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FHXCQBGTTC5E4RC72GJQ5FPGDEQ%2F&h=8350926c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/HXCQBGTTC5E4RC72GJQ5FPGDEQ/</a>"},{"pid":"954d3ca54b4b6d81b648342d779d63886a2b520f","tid":2432434,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"熱狗話呢啲黃屍豬係買贖罪券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036d9dcd6a28f7f24ea4be691c9a55e721a03b9a","tid":2432434,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬥長命"},{"pid":"dc9b9d2cefa701be8ca56602d3a79fecc700337b","tid":2432434,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"平時送幾粒鐘車食風又唔見啲黃屍豬送暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2343be18f34572a0d25670ce22abe237c1515d2","tid":2432434,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b98b574cfdddf62114ddf0be1c57278bd73aae","tid":2432434,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"等睇吹毛求疵同鬥黃"},{"pid":"366a0c3d0f67ee7ca50c8d4a2e975c4fcafbfa14","tid":2432434,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"70歲 ! 多謝每位付出手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces